---+ ML Features

---++ Feature list

Features with (i) are already implemented

   * Text length
   * Nb of paragraphs
   * Nb of sentence
   * Longest / shortest sentence
   * Nb of token
   * Longest / (shortest) token (shortest token will mostly be 2)
   * Nb of stopwords
   * Nb of incorrect words (Spellchecker)
   * Nb of Inserts/Deleltes/Replaces/...
   * Nb of links (internal / external)
   * (i) Char distribution (max bi-gram)
   * (i) Longest char sequence
   * (i) Compression rate
   * (i) Upper case ratio
   * term frequency
   * pronoun frequency
   * pronoun impact
   * vulgarism frequency
   * vulgarism impact
   * replacement similarity
   * context relation (keywords similarity)
   * <strike>anonymity</strike> (no data)
   * <strike>comment length</strike> (no data)
   * <strike>edits per user</strike> (no data)